sql_json.natural_language: Pull all emails from brenda@statpackkzn.co.za to anyone at Lineage this week.
sql_json.generated_sql: SELECT messageId, threadId, fromEmail, subject, sentAt, snippet FROM email_search_index WHERE fromEmail = 'brenda@statpackkzn.co.za' AND 'lineagecoffee.com' IN UNNEST(toEmails) AND sentAt >= TIMESTAMP_SUB(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), INTERVAL 7 DAY) ORDER BY sentAt DESC LIMIT 1;
